      • apply

        public MSCA apply​(MSCA aut)
        invokes the synthesis method for synthesising the choreography
        Specified by:
        apply in interface java.util.function.Function<T extends Object,T extends Object>
        Parameters:
        aut - the plant automaton to which the synthesis is performed
        Returns:
        the synthesised choreography, removing only one transition violating the branching condition each time no further updates are possible. The transition to remove is chosen nondeterministically.
